* Iron Raptor snarled.
< Sure! Leave it to you to take my pray away from me and make me find a new 
one!>
She wasn't exactly too happy about that but at least she could reach 
FireBlade from where she was.
Snapping her head towards the other transformer and takes a few steps 
towards him and rises high onto her hind legs, then bringing her head and 
neck down so that she could curl around him and trap him.
Just as she had done to Zenyak all those months ago.
So she moved to surround him with her body before snapping her head with 
open jaws down towards his shoulder.*
